## Fix 3 — ObjectId Param Validation ✅

`GET /api/properties/not-an-id` now returns immediately:
```json
{
  "success": false,
  "errors": [{ "field": "id", "message": "Invalid id format." }]
}
```
No database round-trip. Applied to every `/:id` and `/:propertyId` route:
- `GET /api/properties/:id`
- `PUT /api/properties/:id`
- `DELETE /api/properties/:id`
- `PATCH /api/properties/:id/status`
- `POST /api/properties/:id/images`
- `GET /api/favorites/:propertyId/status`
- `POST /api/favorites/:propertyId`
- `DELETE /api/favorites/:propertyId`

